#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:hotel.product_template_12
msgid ""
"A wonderful selection of local products<br>Sweet and salty taste<br>Fresh "
"fruits and vegetables<br>Locally roasted Italian coffee<br>Veggie and vegan "
"available"
msgstr ""
"Pilihan luar biasa produk-produk lokal<br>Rasa manis dan asin<br>Buah dan "
"sayuran segar<br>Kopi Italia yang dipanggan lokal<br>Veggie dan vegan "
"tersedia"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Access to more details clicking the slot."
msgstr "Klik slot ini untuk melihat detail lengkapnya."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Add a line with Dinner Tray or an Airport Shuttle and update the counts as "
"per guest\n"
"                request."
msgstr ""
"Tambahkan baris dengan Dinner Tray atau Airport Shuttle dan perbarui "
"jumlahnya sesuai permintaan\n"
"                tamu."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Add here as many of them as needed."
msgstr "Tambahkan di sini sebanyak mungkin yang dibutuhkan."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Add some products to the ongoing order and send it to the preparation "
"display and\n"
"                bring them to your guests."
msgstr ""
"Tambahkan beberapa produk ke pesanan yang sedang berjalan dan kirimkan ke "
"layar persiapan, lalu\n"
"                sajikan kepada tamu Anda."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Adjust the number of stars, leave a comment and send it!"
msgstr "Sesuaikan jumlah bintang, beri komentar, lalu kirimkan!"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Adjust the rental dates, click the book button and then proceed to checkout."
msgstr ""
"Sesuaikan tanggal rental, klik tombol \"pesan\", lalu lanjutkan ke checkout."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Adjusting your offers in consequence"
msgstr "Menyesuaikan penawaran Anda secara berkala"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Again, the <strong>Hotel App </strong>helps you manage the end of the stay!"
msgstr ""
"Sekali lagi, <strong>Aplikasi Hotel </strong> membantu Anda mengelola akhir "
"masa inap!"

#. module: hotel
#: model:product.template,name:hotel.product_template_17
msgid "Airport Shuttle"
msgstr "Shuttle Bandara"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.products_oe_structure_website_sale_products_1
msgid "All our rooms"
msgstr "Semua kamar kami"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternativelly, you can use the Front Desk from the POS App, selecting the\n"
"                    customer, adding any additional services and then paying "
"with the customer\n"
"                    account. At the end of the stay the customer account "
"will be charged as well."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga bisa menggunakan Front Desk dari Aplikasi POS, pilih\n"
"                    pelanggan, tambahkan layanan tambahannya, lalu bayar "
"menggunakan akun\n"
"                    pelanggan. Pada akhir periode menginap, akun pelanggan "
"juga akan ditagih."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively to individual resource blocking slots described earlier, you "
"can select a resource this leave applies to."
msgstr ""
"Selain slot blocking sumber daya satuan yang dijelaskan sebelumnya, Anda "
"dapat memilih sumber daya yang berlaku untuk cuti ini."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively, switch to the list view, and then change the resource.<br/"
">Be\n"
"                    careful not to double book a resource with such change!"
msgstr ""
"Anda juga bisa beralih ke tampilan daftar, lalu mengubah sumber dayanya.<br/>"
"Berhati-hatilah\n"
"                    agar tidak memesan sumber daya dua kali dengan perubahan "
"tersebut!"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively, switch to the list view, which is more suitable if the "
"booking is\n"
"                    not during the visualized date range and update the "
"booking date range."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga bisa beralih ke tampilan daftar, yang lebih cocok jika pemesanan\n"
"                    tidak dalam rentang tanggal yang ditampilkan, dan "
"memperbarui rentang tanggal pemesanan."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively, type in the search bar and select the appropriate filter."
msgstr "Atau, ketik di kolom pencarian dan pilih filter yang sesuai."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can create a slot as placeholder from the planning "
"directly:"
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat membuat slot sebagai placeholder langsung dari perencanaan:"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "An automation is setup for an email to be sent automatically for you."
msgstr ""
"Sistem otomatisasi telah disiapkan agar email dikirimkan secara otomatis "
"untuk Anda."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Any time you create a new survey and save it with the setting \"is customer "
"satisfaction survey\", previous ones\n"
"                    will be archived so that it becomes your new default "
"survey."
msgstr ""
"Setiap kali Anda membuat survei baru dan menyimpannya dengan pengaturan "
"\"adalah survei kepuasan pelanggan\", survei sebelumnya\n"
"                    akan diarsipkan sehingga menjadi survei default yang "
"baru."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Anyone can create a portal account on your database.<br/>Open your website "
"home page\n"
"                in a private tab to do so."
msgstr ""
"Siapa pun dapat membuat akun portal di database Anda.<br/>Buka halaman "
"beranda website\n"
"                di tab pribadi untuk melakukannya."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Assign them a resource, which helps you keeping track."
msgstr "Tetapkan sumber daya kepadanya untuk membantu pelacakan."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"At any time during their stay, open their rental order from the Hotel App."
msgstr ""
"Kapan pun selama periode inap tamu, buka rental order dari Aplikasi Hotel."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"At any time from the guest order, use the Send message capability in the "
"chatter\n"
"                    to exchange with your guest."
msgstr ""
"Kapan pun dari pesanan tamu, gunakan fitur Kirim pesan di Chatter\n"
"                    untuk berkomunikasi dengan tamu Anda."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"At any time you can adjust the city tax count delivered by re-opening the "
"city tax widget clicking the City Tax button on the guest order."
msgstr ""
"Jumlah pajak kota yang ditampilkan dapat disesuaikan kapan saja dengan "
"membuka kembali widget pajak kota, mengeklik tombol Pajak Kota pada pesanan "
"tamu."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "At the end of their stay, your guests will pay for all those extras."
msgstr ""
"Pada akhir periode inap, tamu Anda akan membayar semua tambahan tersebut."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Bar &amp; Restaurant and extra services"
msgstr "Bar &amp; Restoran dan layanan tambahan"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Beyond daily operations, the Steering menu serves as the \"Captain’s "
"Bridge\" of your hotel. It provides a 500-day horizon to anticipate market "
"trends, manage risks, and optimize your revenue."
msgstr ""
"Selain untuk operasi harian, menu Steering berfungsi sebagai \"Pusat "
"Kendali\" hotel Anda. Fitur ini memberikan insight 500 hari ke depan untuk "
"mengantisipasi tren pasar, mengelola risiko, dan mengoptimalkan pendapatan "
"Anda."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Blocking resources"
msgstr "Blocking sumber daya"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Booking a room"
msgstr "Memesan kamar"

#. module: hotel
#: model:product.template,name:hotel.product_template_12
msgid "Breakfast"
msgstr "Breakfast"

#. module: hotel
#: model:product.template,name:hotel.product_template_14
msgid "Breakfast Tray"
msgstr "Breakfast Tray"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"By uploading this module's demo data, your database has been filled with a "
"few products,\n"
"            sale orders and more."
msgstr ""
"Dengan mengunggah data demo modul ini, database Anda telah diisi dengan "
"beberapa produk,\n"
"            sales order, dan lainnya."

#. module: hotel
#: model:product.template,name:hotel.product_template_16
msgid "Champagne Bottle"
msgstr "Botol Champagne"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Charge your guests"
msgstr "Membuat tagihan untuk tamu"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.view_page_contactus
msgid ""
"Chat with us or fill in this form to get information about anything related "
"to our rooms or the palace.<br/><br/>"
msgstr ""
"Hubungi kami lewat obrolan atau isi formulir ini untuk mendapatkan informasi "
"tentang kamar atau hotel ini.<br/><br/>"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Check and adjust if needed the number of guest who stayed in each room. Then "
"confirm the number of city tax to be charged, which updated the delivered "
"city tax count."
msgstr ""
"Periksa dan sesuaikan (bila perlu) jumlah tamu yang menginap di setiap "
"kamar. Setelah itu, konfirmasi jumlah pajak kota yang akan dikenakan. "
"Nantinya, jumlah pajak kota yang telah disampaikan akan diperbarui."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Check guests in"
msgstr "Melakukan check-in tamu"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Check guests out"
msgstr "Melakukan check-out tamu"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Check information and then confirm the booking."
msgstr "Periksa informasi, lalu konfirmasi pemesanan."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"City Taxes are to be billed to spent nights in practice and not in theory "
"and are counted as the sum of nights each guest stayed."
msgstr ""
"Pajak Kota harus ditagih berdasarkan jumlah malam aktual yang dihabiskan, "
"bukan secara teoritis, dan dihitung sebagai jumlah total malam yang "
"dihabiskan oleh setiap tamu."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click one of the room to book."
msgstr "Klik salah satu kamar untuk dipesan."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Click the Check in button to confirm they are now staying at your place!"
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol Check in untuk mengonfirmasi bahwa tamu kini menginap di tempat "
"Anda!"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click the Check out button to capture they return you the keys."
msgstr "Klik tombol Check out untuk merekam pengembalian kunci."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Click the Create Order to open the order form."
msgstr "Klik Buat Pesanan untuk membuka formulir pesanan."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Click the Pay with demo button, and then Pay button to mimic the payment."
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol Bayar dengan demo, lalu tombol Bayar untuk menguji coba "
"pembayaran."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Click the Settle PoS Orders button to add the corresponding order lines."
msgstr ""
"Klik tombol Selesaikan Pesanan POS untuk menambahkan baris pesanan yang "
"bersangkutan."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Click the tail of the corresponding booking and drag it to the requested "
"date."
msgstr ""
"Klik ujung pemesanan yang bersangkutan dan seret ke tanggal yang diminta."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Configure the email delay as you wish the email to be sent after the guest "
"checkout."
msgstr ""
"Atur jeda email sesuai keinginan agar email dikirim setelah tamu melakukan "
"checkout."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.template_footer_minimalist
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.view_page_contactus
msgid "Contact us"
msgstr "Hubungi kami"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create a new leave selecting the appropriate working schedule, the one from "
"your stay resources."
msgstr ""
"Buat cuti baru dengan memilih jadwal kerja yang sesuai, yang tercantum pada "
"sumber daya akomodasi Anda."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Create a new leave the same way as previously, but this time specify the "
"resource this applies to."
msgstr ""
"Buat cuti baru dengan cara yang sama seperti sebelumnya, tetapi kali ini "
"tentukan sumber daya yang berlaku untuk cuti tersebut."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Created offers are assigned no company nor branch (default behavior).<br/>As "
"a result, they are available from all companies and branches, as well as all "
"websites from those."
msgstr ""
"Penawaran yang sudah dibuat tidak ditetapkan ke perusahaan atau cabang mana "
"pun (perilaku default).<br/>Dengan demikian, penawaran tersebut tersedia di "
"semua perusahaan dan cabang, serta semua website dari perusahaan atau cabang "
"tersebut."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Define start and end date time and save your leave."
msgstr "Tentukan tanggal dan waktu mulai serta akhir, lalu simpan cuti."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Deliver extra services"
msgstr "Memberikan layanan tambahan"

#. module: hotel
#: model:product.template,name:hotel.product_template_15
msgid "Dinner Tray"
msgstr "Dinner Tray"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Discover more about Odoo by diving into our"
msgstr "Temukan lebih banyak mengenai Odoo dengan masuk ke"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Discover the basics of this package and explore all the possibilities Odoo "
"offers to\n"
"            improve your experience."
msgstr ""
"Temukan standar paket ini dan temukan semua tawaran Odoo\n"
"            untuk meningkatkan pengalaman Anda."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Don't be limited to those examples, you could have a gym area available to "
"members or a\n"
"            spa with massages!"
msgstr ""
"Jangan terbatas pada contoh-contoh tersebut. Anda bisa memiliki area gym "
"untuk anggota atau\n"
"            spa dengan layanan pijat!"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Don't forget to send them their invoice!"
msgstr "Jangan lupa kirimkan faktur kepada pelanggan!"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"During an available period, click, drag and drop on a room line to create a "
"slot."
msgstr ""
"Selama periode yang tersedia, klik, seret, dan lepaskan di baris kamar untuk "
"membuat slot."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Each company can have its own website!"
msgstr "Setiap perusahaan dapat memiliki website sendiri!"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.view_page_home
msgid ""
"Each stone was carved from the surrounding cliffs, each beam of larch wood "
"carried up the slopes by mule. The architecture blended <b><span "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Belle Époque elegance</span></b> with <b><span "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">mountain authenticity</span></b>, creating an "
"atmosphere that felt both majestic and deeply intimate."
msgstr ""
"Setiap batu diukir dari tebing di sekitarnya, setiap balok kayu larch "
"diangkut melewati lereng dengan keledai. Arsitekturnya memadukan <b><span "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">keanggunan Belle Époque</span></b> dengan <b><span "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">keaslian pegunungan</span></b>, menciptakan suasana "
"yang terasa megah sekaligus akrab."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Employee assignations"
msgstr "Penugasan karyawan"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Employee would open the tasks from their hand and update the status until "
"Clean."
msgstr ""
"Karyawan akan membuka tugas dari catatannya sendiri dan memperbarui "
"statusnya hingga Bersih."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.view_page_home
msgid "End date"
msgstr "Tanggal berakhir"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Example: A room for 2 is booked for 4 nights, two guests were here for the "
"first three nights but only one stayed the last night. Then the guests x "
"nights is 2x3+1x1=7."
msgstr ""
"Contoh: Kamar untuk 2 orang dipesan selama 4 malam, dua tamu menginap selama "
"tiga malam pertama, tapi hanya satu orang yang menginap pada malam terakhir. "
"Dengan demikian, penghitungan tamu x malam adalah 2x3+1x1=7."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.template_footer_minimalist
msgid "Follow us"
msgstr "Ikuti kami"

#. module: hotel
#: model:product.template,name:hotel.product_template_11
msgid "Free Cancellation"
msgstr "Pembatalan Gratis"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"From the <strong>Hotel App</strong>, you can manage your bookings.<br/>The\n"
"            Hotel App relies on the Rental and Planning Apps binding, with a "
"few\n"
"            customizations."
msgstr ""
"Dari <strong>Aplikasi Hotel</strong> , Anda dapat mengelola pemesanan.<br/>"
"Aplikasi\n"
"            Hotel bergantung pada binding Aplikasi Rental dan Perencanaan, "
"dengan beberapa\n"
"            penyesuaian."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"From the Roles sections, you can select the companies and branches this "
"employee shall have access to as well as the default one."
msgstr ""
"Dari bagian Peran, Anda dapat memilih perusahaan dan cabang yang dapat "
"diakses oleh karyawan ini serta yang menjadi default."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"From the search bar select the Today filter to see to check in and to check "
"out\n"
"                orders."
msgstr ""
"Dari kolom pencarian, pilih filter Hari Ini untuk melihat order untuk check "
"in dan\n"
"                check out."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "From there you can add new companies."
msgstr "Dari sana, Anda dapat menambahkan perusahaan baru."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.view_page_home
msgid ""
"Guided by this vision, Norris chose a secluded plateau overlooking a "
"pristine valley, where the silence of the pines mingled with the distant "
"echo of cowbells. There, with the help of local craftsmen and artisans, he "
"began to build what would become the <b><span class=\"text-o-color-1\">Grand "
"Norris Palace</span></b>."
msgstr ""
"Berangkat dari visi ini, Norris memilih dataran tinggi terpencil yang "
"menghadap ke lembah yang belum terjamah, di mana keheningan pohon pinus "
"berpadu dengan gema lonceng sapi dari kejauhan. Di sana, dengan bantuan para "
"pengrajin dan seniman lokal, ia mulai membangun cikal bakal <b><span "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Grand Norris Palace</span></b>."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Hello there!"
msgstr "Halo!"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.view_page_home
msgid ""
"Here, nature reigns supreme. Mornings begin with the scent of larch and the "
"sound of distant waterfalls; evenings end under a canopy of stars untouched "
"by city lights. The Palace's terraces open onto sweeping views of the <span "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>Mont Blanc massif</b></span> and the <b><span "
"class=\"text-o-color-1\">Trient Glacier</span></b>, offering a sense of "
"peace that feels almost sacred."
msgstr ""
"Di sini, alam menguasai semuanya. Pagi hari dimulai dengan aroma pohon larch "
"dan suara air terjun dari kejauhan; senja berakhir dengan langit berbintang "
"yang tak tersentuh cahaya kota. Teras Palace ini menghadap ke bentangan "
"<span class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>pegunungan Mont Blanc</b></span> dan <b>"
"<span class=\"text-o-color-1\">Gletser Trient</span></b> , menghadirkan "
"kedamaian yang nyaris terasa suci."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.template_footer_minimalist
msgid "Home"
msgstr "Beranda"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.res_config_settings_form_view_inherited
msgid "Hotel"
msgstr "Hotel"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If not OK, then click the contact, fill in the Identity section and save "
"the\n"
"                contact."
msgstr ""
"Jika tidak sesuai, klik kontak tersebut, isi bagian Identitas, dan simpan\n"
"                kontak."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If they paid orders at any point of sale with their customer account, their "
"customer account due amount will be displayed as well as a button for you to "
"settle the associated orders."
msgstr ""
"Jika pelanggan membayar pesanan di POS menggunakan akun pelanggannya, jumlah "
"tagihan akun pelanggannya akan ditampilkan beserta tombol untuk "
"menyelesaikan pesanan terkait."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If using the house keeping approver setting, designated\n"
"                    approvers can check each room and set their state to "
"ready to close the tasks."
msgstr ""
"Jika menggunakan pengaturan approver housekeeping, approver yang ditentukan\n"
"                    dapat memeriksa setiap ruangan dan menetapkan statusnya "
"menjadi siap untuk menutup tugas."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you want to execute a practical guided tour of this module, you should "
"Import\n"
"                    demo data and try the Demo - Use Case (In the next "
"Knowledge Article)"
msgstr ""
"Bila Anda ingin menjalankan tur praktis modul ini, Anda harus mengimpor\n"
"                    data demo dan coba Demo - Kasus Penggunaan (Di Artikel "
"Pengetahuan berikutnya)"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"If you're not certain customers have ongoing bookings, before charging their "
"customer accounts, open their contact details from their menu (from the "
"customer list) and ask for the room they stay in.<br/>Note: Their room is "
"listed in the Guests tab of their order."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda tidak yakin apakah pelanggan memiliki pemesanan aktif, sebelum "
"menagih akun pelanggan, buka detail kontak pelanggan tersebut dari menu "
"(dari daftar pelanggan) dan tanyakan kamarnya.<br/>Catatan: Kamar pelanggan "
"tercantum di tab Tamu pada pesanannya."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "In any case, the resources are company and branch dependent."
msgstr "Bagaimana pun, sumber daya bergantung pada perusahaan dan cabang."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"In any case, you may have written records in journals which are not delete-"
"able and which\n"
"            might be an issue for your traceability."
msgstr ""
"Bagaimana pun juga, Anda mungkin memiliki catatan tertulis di jurnal yang "
"tidak dapat dihapus dan yang\n"
"            mungkin menjadi masalah bagi pelacakan Anda."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"In case you outsource or rely more heavily on suppliers, the "
"<strong>Purchase App</strong>\n"
"                will help you to manage those aspects."
msgstr ""
"Jika Anda menggunakan outsourcing atau sangat bergantung pada supplier, "
"<strong>Aplikasi Purchase</strong>\n"
"                akan membantu pengelolaan aspek-aspek tersebut."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"In the Options tab, you can see it is made the customer satisfaction survey "
"in the participants section."
msgstr ""
"Di tab Opsi, akan ada survei kepuasan pelanggan yang terbuat di bagian "
"peserta."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"It enables each place manager to adjust the stay offers with greater "
"flexibility without impacting other places."
msgstr ""
"Hal ini memungkinkan setiap manajer lokasi untuk menyesuaikan penawaran inap "
"dengan lebih fleksibel tanpa memengaruhi lokasi lain."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Keep your guests satisfied"
msgstr "Memastikan tamu selalu puas"

#. module: hotel
#: model:product.template,name:hotel.product_template_8
msgid "La Claudia"
msgstr "La Claudia"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:hotel.product_template_8
msgid ""
"La Claudia invites you into a bright and contemporary environment, where "
"soft colors and chic furnishings enhance your sense of well-being. Whether "
"you are unwinding after an active day or enjoying a quiet morning with a "
"view, this room brings together elegance, space, and serenity for an "
"unforgettable stay."
msgstr ""
"La Claudia mengajak Anda menikmati suasana cerah dan kontemporer, dengan "
"warna-warna lembut dan perabotan elegan untuk meningkatkan kenyamanan Anda. "
"Baik untuk bersantai setelah hari yang sibuk maupun menikmati pagi yang "
"tenang dengan pemandangan indah, kamar ini memadukan keanggunan, kelapangan, "
"dan ketenangan untuk pengalaman menginap yang tak terlupakan."

#. module: hotel
#: model:product.template,name:hotel.product_template_9
msgid "La Maria"
msgstr "La Maria"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:hotel.product_template_9
msgid ""
"La Maria welcomes you with a bright and refined atmosphere, blending modern "
"comfort with subtle alpine charm. Soft textures, elegant furnishings, and "
"thoughtfully designed spaces create the ideal setting to relax and recharge. "
"With its soothing ambiance and premium amenities, La Maria offers a serene "
"escape in the heart of the Swiss Alps."
msgstr ""
"La Maria menyambut Anda dengan suasana yang cerah dan elegan, memadukan "
"kenyamanan modern dengan pesona pegunungan Alpen yang tenang. Tekstur "
"lembut, perabotan elegan, dan ruang yang dirancang dengan cermat menciptakan "
"suasana yang ideal untuk bersantai dan memulihkan tenaga. Dengan suasananya "
"yang menenangkan dan fasilitas premium, La Maria menawarkan tempat liburan "
"yang tenang di tengah Pegunungan Alpen Swiss."

#. module: hotel
#: model:product.template,name:hotel.product_template_10
msgid "La Nina"
msgstr "La Nina"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:product.template,description_ecommerce:hotel.product_template_10
msgid ""
"La Nina is a sophisticated haven combining contemporary elegance with the "
"charm of alpine living. Its thoughtfully curated decor, premium bedding, and "
"high-end comforts create a serene environment for true rest. Enjoy the "
"mountain view from your private space, indulge in a moment of calm, and "
"experience a stay where every detail is designed for your well-being."
msgstr ""
"La Nina adalah tempat liburan berkelas yang memadukan keanggunan kontemporer "
"dengan pesona kehidupan pegunungan. Dekorasi yang dirancang dengan cermat, "
"tempat tidur berkualitas premium, dan kenyamanan kelas atas menciptakan "
"suasana yang tenang untuk istirahat yang sesungguhnya. Nikmati pemandangan "
"pegunungan dari ruang pribadi Anda, manjakan diri dengan momen ketenangan, "
"dan rasakan pengalaman menginap dengan setiap detail yang dirancang untuk "
"ketenangan Anda."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Leaving a review"
msgstr "Memberikan ulasan"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Let's book a room!"
msgstr "Ayo pesan kamar!"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage your accounting easier than ever with a completely integrated "
"environment i<font class=\"text-o-color-5\">n </font><strong>\n"
"                    <font class=\"text-o-color-5\">Accounting App</font>\n"
"                </strong><font class=\"text-o-color-5\">.</font>"
msgstr ""
"Kelola akuntansi dengan lebih mudah dalam sistem yang sepenuhnya "
"terintegrasi d<font class=\"text-o-color-5\">i </font><strong>\n"
"                    <font class=\"text-o-color-5\">Aplikasi Akuntansi</font>"
"\n"
"                </strong><font class=\"text-o-color-5\">.</font>"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Managing scarcity with availability"
msgstr "Mengelola kelangkaan dengan ketersediaan"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Managing your businesses"
msgstr "Mengelola bisnis Anda"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Monitoring success with occupancy"
msgstr "Memantau keberhasilan dengan okupansi"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Now that they relax, you can offer extra services to make your guests fill "
"even more\n"
"            comfortable!"
msgstr ""
"Setelah tamu bisa bersantai, Anda dapat menawarkan layanan tambahan agar "
"mereka merasa\n"
"            lebih nyaman!"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Now that you have several companies or branches, you may want some of your "
"employees to access only to some of them in case they always work in some of "
"your places."
msgstr ""
"Setelah memiliki beberapa perusahaan atau cabang, Anda mungkin ingin "
"membatasi aksesnya hanya untuk karyawan tertentu sesuai dengan lokasi "
"kerjanya."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Odoo offers you infinite possibilities, such as:"
msgstr "Odoo menawarkan Anda kemungkinan yang tanpa batas, seperti:"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free\n"
"            to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test everything "
"around!"
msgstr ""
"Tentu saja, ini hanyalah gambaran umum fitur-fitur yang termasuk di paket "
"ini. Jangan ragu\n"
"             untuk menambahkan aplikasi baru, menghapus/memodifikasi data "
"demo, dan menguji semua yang Anda lihat!"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"On a daily basis, house keeping tasks are created depending\n"
"                    the current stays."
msgstr ""
"Setiap hari, tugas-tugas house keeping dibuat tergantung\n"
"                    periode inap saat ini."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "On a resource to block line, click, drag and drop to create a slot."
msgstr ""
"Untuk membuat blocking baris, klik, seret, dan lepaskan sumber daya untuk "
"membuat slot."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "On top of guest and stay management, you need to keep the place clean!"
msgstr ""
"Selain pengelolaan tamu dan periode inap, kebersihan lokasi juga harus "
"dijaga!"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Once confirmed, the payment is done and the order booked seamlessly!"
msgstr ""
"Setelah dikonfirmasi, pembayaran selesai dan pesanan dipesan dengan lancar!"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once defined, you can switch between companies or branches from the company "
"selector at the top right of your screen.<br/>This will expose depending on "
"where you are, only the selected companies and branches data."
msgstr ""
"Setelah ditentukan, Anda dapat mengubah perusahaan atau cabang dari pemilih "
"perusahaan di pojok kanan atas layar.<br/>Tergantung di mana Anda berada, "
"hal ini hanya akan menampilkan data perusahaan dan cabang yang dipilih."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once done adding all the necessary rooms, click on a recently added slot and "
"then\n"
"                click the rental order link."
msgstr ""
"Setelah selesai menambahkan semua kamar yang diperlukan, klik slot yang baru "
"ditambahkan, lalu\n"
"                klik tautan rental order."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once done, let's click, drag and drop on another room line to create a slot."
msgstr ""
"Setelah selesai, klik, seret, dan lepaskan pada baris kamar lain untuk "
"membuat slot."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Once done, logged in as a portal user."
msgstr "Setelah selesai, masuk sebagai user portal."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once your guest order is all set after check out, create an invoice from "
"their order."
msgstr ""
"Begitu pesanan tamu Anda selesai setelah checkout, buat faktur dari "
"pesanannya."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open a room page from the website and scroll down to the Customer Reviews "
"section."
msgstr ""
"Buka halaman kamar dari website dan gulir ke bawah ke bagian Ulasan "
"Pelanggan."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open now, the Tasks from the accommodation app, House Keeping menu.<br/>This "
"is\n"
"                the daily list of house keeping tasks to be tackled."
msgstr ""
"Buka sekarang, menu Tugas dari aplikasi akomodasi, menu House Keeping.<br/>"
"Ini adalah\n"
"                daftar harian tugas house keeping yang harus diselesaikan."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open one, assign it to an employee to plan the house keeping of the day."
msgstr ""
"Buka satu, tugaskan kepada seorang karyawan untuk merencanakan house keeping "
"pada hari tersebut."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the <strong>Settings App</strong> and reach the companies from the menu "
"Users &amp; Companies."
msgstr ""
"Buka <strong>Aplikasi Pengaturan</strong> dan akses perusahaan melalui menu "
"User &amp; Perusahaan."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the <strong>Settings App</strong> and reach the users from the menu "
"Users &amp; Companies."
msgstr ""
"Buka <strong>Aplikasi Pengaturan</strong> dan akses user melalui menu User "
"&amp; Perusahaan."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the <strong>Website App</strong> and navigate to the Rooms."
msgstr "Buka <strong>Aplikasi Website</strong> dan buka Kamar."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the Board from the accommodation app, House Keeping menu.<br/>Here you "
"have an\n"
"                overview of the cleanness state of your resources."
msgstr ""
"Buka Papan dari aplikasi akomodasi, menu House Keeping.<br/>Di sini, ada\n"
"                gambaran umum tentang kondisi kebersihan sumber daya Anda."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the Hotel App and navigate to the Configuration / Leaves menu."
msgstr "Buka Aplikasi Hotel dan buka menu Konfigurasi / Cuti."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the Hotel App and then navigate to the orders from the menu."
msgstr "Buka Aplikasi Hotel, lalu buka pesanan dari menu."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the Hotel App to appreciate the currently planned bookings with the\n"
"                Schedule."
msgstr ""
"Buka Aplikasi Hotel untuk melihat pemesanan yang sedang direncanakan "
"melalui\n"
"                Jadwal."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the POS App and select one of the register, the Bar for example."
msgstr "Buka Aplikasi POS dan pilih salah satu kasir, misalnya Bar."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the Steering menu and select Availability."
msgstr "Buka menu Steering dan pilih Ketersediaan."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the Steering menu and select Occupancy."
msgstr "Buka menu Steering dan pilih Okupansi."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the Survey App to find the customer satisfaction survey."
msgstr "Buka Aplikasi Survei untuk mengakses survei kepuasan pelanggan."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the door for more custom workflows and actions with the power of "
"<strong>Studio\n"
"                App</strong>."
msgstr ""
"Bukakan peluang untuk alur kerja dan tindakan yang lebih spesifik dengan "
"kebutuhan Anda bersama <strong>Aplikasi\n"
"                Studio</strong>."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the order of you just arrived guests."
msgstr "Buka pesanan tamu yang baru saja tiba."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open your guest order from the Hotel App."
msgstr "Buka pesanan tamu dari Aplikasi Hotel."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Organize your employees' schedules with<font class=\"text-o-color-5\"> "
"<strong>\n"
"                Planning</strong></font><strong>\n"
"                    <font class=\"text-o-color-5\"> App</font>\n"
"                </strong><font class=\"text-o-color-5\">.</font>"
msgstr ""
"Atur jadwal karyawan Anda dengan<font class=\"text-o-color-5\"> <strong>\n"
"                Aplikasi</strong></font><strong>\n"
"                    <font class=\"text-o-color-5\"> Perencanaan</font>\n"
"                </strong><font class=\"text-o-color-5\"> .</font>"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.view_page_contactus
msgid ""
"Our team will be delighted to assist you and will respond to your message "
"within 2 open&amp;nbsp;days"
msgstr ""
"Tim kami akan dengan senang hati membantu dan menanggapi pesan Anda dalam "
"waktu 2 hari kerja"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.view_page_home
msgid ""
"Perched high above the valley of <b><span class=\"text-o-color-1\">Orsières</"
"span></b>, in the enchanting <b><span class=\"text-o-color-1\">Valais "
"region</span></b> of Switzerland, the <b><span class=\"text-o-"
"color-1\">Grand Norris Palace</span></b> enjoys one of the most breathtaking "
"settings in the Alps.&amp;nbsp;"
msgstr ""
"Terletak tinggi di atas lembah <b><span class=\"text-o-color-1\">Orsières</"
"span></b>, di <b><span class=\"text-o-color-1\">wilayah Valais</span></b> "
"yang memesona di Swiss, <b><span class=\"text-o-color-1\">Grand Norris "
"Palace</span></b> berlokasi di salah satu pemandangan paling menakjubkan di "
"Pegunungan Alpen.&amp;nbsp;"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Proceed to the payment with your terminal and set the invoice as paid."
msgstr ""
"Lanjutkan ke pembayaran dengan terminal Anda dan ubah status faktur sebagai "
"dibayar."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Reach us"
msgstr "Hubungi kami"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Record guest identity"
msgstr "Mencatat identitas tamu"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Recording the guest attendance is an obligation in numerous countries."
msgstr "Pencatatan kehadiran tamu merupakan kewajiban di banyak negara."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.template_footer_minimalist
msgid "Rooms"
msgstr "Kamar"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Save the order with those extra services."
msgstr "Simpan pesanan dengan layanan tambahan tersebut."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Select one of your employee."
msgstr "Pilih salah satu karyawan Anda."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Select or create a customer and then confirm the booking!"
msgstr "Pilih atau buat pelanggan, lalu konfirmasi pemesanan!"

#. module: hotel
#: model:pos.category,name:hotel.pos_category_1
msgid "Service"
msgstr "Layanan"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Setup company or branch specific offers when relevant."
msgstr "Siapkan penawaran khusus perusahaan atau cabang jika relevan."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Share your stay offers across your companies and branches (default behavior);"
msgstr ""
"Bagikan penawaran menginap Anda di seluruh perusahaan dan cabang (perilaku "
"default);"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.view_page_home
msgid "Start date"
msgstr "Tanggal mulai"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Still from the Hotel App Schedule, simply drag and drop a booking to "
"another\n"
"                more comfortable room!"
msgstr ""
"Masih dari Jadwal Aplikasi Hotel, cukup seret dan lepaskan pemesanan ke\n"
"                kamar lain yang lebih nyaman!"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Still from their Rental Order, open the Guests tab."
msgstr "Masih dari Rental Order pelanggan, buka tab Tamu."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.view_page_contactus
msgid "Submit"
msgstr "Kirim"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.view_page_home
msgid ""
"Surrounded by <span class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>snow-capped peaks, pine "
"forests, and crystal-clear mountain lakes</b>,</span> the Palace overlooks a "
"panorama that changes with every season <em>from the golden glow of autumn "
"to the soft, shimmering silence of winter.</em>"
msgstr ""
"Dikelilingi <span class=\"text-o-color-1\"><b>puncak gunung berselimut "
"salju, hutan pinus, dan danau pegunungan yang jernih</b>,</span> Hotel ini "
"menghadap panorama yang berganti rupa setiap musim <em>dari cantiknya "
"keemasan musim gugur hingga keheningan musim dingin yang lembut dan "
"berkilauan.</em>"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Gantt chart is color-coded to reflect on the availability for you to "
"work on filling in."
msgstr ""
"Bagan Gantt diberi kode warna untuk menunjukkan ketersediaan untuk diisi."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Gantt chart is color-coded to reflect on the occupancy, the higher the "
"better."
msgstr ""
"Bagan Gantt diberi kode warna untuk mencerminkan okupansi; makin tinggi, "
"makin baik."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The Occupancy view allows you to visualize your \"Sales Success\". It "
"answers one simple question: <i>How well am I filling my hotel?</i>"
msgstr ""
"Tampilan Okupansi menyajikan visualisasi \"Keberhasilan Sales\" Anda. "
"Tampilan ini menjawab satu pertanyaan sederhana: <i>Seberapa baik tingkat "
"hunian hotel saya?</i>"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.view_page_home
msgid ""
"The estate lies at the crossroads of ancient mountain paths once used by "
"shepherds and traders crossing into Italy. Today, it remains a place of "
"quiet majesty, far from the noise of the world yet easily accessible from "
"<b><span class=\"text-o-color-1\">Verbier, Montreux, or Geneva</span></b>. "
"Guests arrive along a winding alpine road that reveals, turn after turn, a "
"landscape of pure wonder — until, at last, the turrets of the Grand Norris "
"Palace emerge against the sky."
msgstr ""
"Hotel ini terletak di persimpangan jalur pegunungan kuno yang dulu digunakan "
"oleh para gembala dan pedagang yang melintasi perbatasan ke Italia. Saat "
"ini, tempat ini tetap tenang dan megah, jauh dari hiruk pikuk dunia, tapi "
"mudah dijangkau dari <b><span class=\"text-o-color-1\">Verbier, Montreux, "
"atau Jenewa</span></b>. Para tamu akan melalui jalan pegunungan yang "
"berkelok-kelok yang di tikungan demi tikungannya menampilkan pemandangan "
"yang sungguh menakjubkan — hingga akhirnya, menara-menara Grand Norris "
"Palace muncul menjulang di langit."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.view_page_home
msgid ""
"The story begins in <b><span class=\"text-o-color-1\">1897</span></b>, when "
"visionary hotelier <b><span class=\"text-o-color-1\">Edmond Norris</span></"
"b> , captivated by the untouched majesty of the Valais mountains, dreamt of "
"creating a sanctuary unlike any other — a place where the rugged purity of "
"the Alps would meet the grace and refinement of European hospitality."
msgstr ""
"Kisah ini bermula pada tahun <b><span class=\"text-o-color-1\">1897</span></"
"b>, ketika pengusaha perhotelan visioner <b><span class=\"text-o-color-1\">"
"Edmond Norris</span></b>, yang terpesona oleh keagungan pegunungan Valais "
"yang belum terjamah, bermimpi menciptakan hotel yang tak tertandingi—tempat "
"di mana kemurnian pegunungan Alpen yang liar berpadu dengan keanggunan dan "
"kehalusan perhotelan Eropa."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The strength of Odoo is to separate the accounting and many other aspects "
"which are company dependent!"
msgstr ""
"Keunggulan Odoo adalah memisahkan akuntansi dan aspek-aspek lainnya yang "
"bergantung pada perusahaan!"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"These all go free in your current subscription; feel free to explore! 🙃"
msgstr ""
"Semua ini bisa Anda akses gratis dengan langgananmu saat ini. Jangan ragu "
"untuk menjelajahinya! 🙃"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"They as well share the same pricing, defined at the stay offer level, which "
"has its pros and cons."
msgstr ""
"Harganya juga sama dan ditentukan pada tingkat penawaran inap. Hal ini "
"sendiri memiliki kelebihan dan kekurangan."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "They want multiple rooms?"
msgstr "Tamu ingin lebih dari satu kamar?"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "They were happy about their stay, let's ask them to leave a review."
msgstr "Pelanggan senang dengan periode inapnya, mari minta ulasan."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "They will balance their customer account during the check out!"
msgstr "Mereka akan menyelesaikan pembayaran kamar saat checkout!"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This blocks simulataneously all resources related to this working schedule "
"during the prescribed period."
msgstr ""
"Hal ini mengeblok semua sumber daya yang terkait dengan jadwal kerja ini "
"secara bersamaan selama periode yang ditentukan."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "This capability is enabled by a setting you can set/unset."
msgstr ""
"Fitur ini diaktifkan melalui pengaturan yang dapat diaktifkan/nonaktifkan."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This setup is relevant in case of place specific offers or when pricing "
"varies between places."
msgstr ""
"Pengaturan ini relevan untuk penawaran di lokasi tertentu atau ketika harga "
"bervariasi di setiap lokasi."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This time click the Add to last order button to add this room to the booking "
"and\n"
"                voila!"
msgstr ""
"Kali ini, klik tombol Tambahkan ke pesanan terakhir untuk menambahkan kamar "
"ini ke pemesanan,\n"
"                dan selesai!"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This time, simply leave a note about the why this is booked and save the "
"slot."
msgstr ""
"Kali ini, cukup buat catatan tentang alasan pemesanan ini dan simpan slotnya."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"To ensure your guests no longer receive the satisfaction survey, you can "
"easily archive it at any time."
msgstr ""
"Untuk memastikan tamu tidak lagi menerima survei kepuasan, Anda dapat "
"mengarsipkannya kapan saja."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Trace guest attendance"
msgstr "Melacak kehadiran tamu"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Two options are now available to you with multiple companies and branches:"
msgstr "Kini tersedia dua opsi bagi Anda dengan beberapa perusahaan dan cabang:"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Type in the customer name in the Schedule search bar filtering by Customer."
msgstr ""
"Ketik nama pelanggan di kolom pencarian Jadwal dengan filter menurut "
"Pelanggan."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Welcome your guests as well from the <strong>Hotel App</strong>."
msgstr "Sambut juga tamu Anda melalui <strong>Aplikasi Hotel</strong>."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "When all is in order, confirm their invoice for payment."
msgstr "Setelah semuanya beres, konfirmasikan faktur untuk pembayaran."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When creating an offer, assign them a company or a branch.<br/>As a result, "
"they are available only for the selected company or branch, and will be "
"available only from its website."
msgstr ""
"Saat membuat penawaran, tetapkan ke perusahaan atau cabang.<br/>Dengan "
"begitu, penawaran tersebut hanya tersedia untuk perusahaan atau cabang yang "
"dipilih, dan hanya dapat diakses melalui website-nya."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"When they ask for the bill, you can charge them directly or add the bill to "
"their\n"
"                customer account.<br/>To do so, open the corresponding order "
"from the table or from\n"
"                the order list and select the customer to charge.<br/>Click "
"the payment and the\n"
"                validation buttons!"
msgstr ""
"Ketika pelanggan meminta tagihan, Anda dapat menagihnya langsung atau "
"menambahkan tagihan ke\n"
"                akun pelanggannya.<br/>Untuk melakukannya, buka pesanan yang "
"bersangkutan dari tabel atau dari\n"
"                daftar pesanan dan pilih pelanggan yang akan ditagih.<br/>"
"Klik tombol pembayaran dan\n"
"                tombol validasi!"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"While Occupancy focuses on what is full, the Availability view focuses on "
"what is left to sell. It is your primary tool for operational safety and "
"\"Scarcity Pricing.\""
msgstr ""
"Sementara Okupansi berfokus pada penuh atau tidaknya kamar, Ketersediaan "
"berfokus pada kamar yang masih bisa dijual. Fitur ini adalah alat utama "
"untuk keamanan operasional dan penetapan \"Harga Kelangkaan\"."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Willing to upgrade a booking?"
msgstr "Ingin upgrade pemesanan?"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"With the create slot for this resource, no overlapping booking slot would be "
"created.<br/>Care about the start and end time or this blockage to make to "
"re-open when suited."
msgstr ""
"Dengan slot pembuatan untuk sumber daya ini, slot pemesanan yang tumpang "
"tindih tidak akan terbuat.<br/>Perhatikan waktu mulai dan berakhir atau "
"blocking ini agar dapat dibuka kembali saat diperlukan."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "Would you like to discuss your Odoo setup with us or go even further?"
msgstr ""
"Apakah Anda ingin mendiskusikan lebih lanjut setup Odoo Anda dengan kami "
"atau melanjutkan tur?"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "You Hotel is online and future guests found it!"
msgstr "Hotel Anda sudah online dan calon tamu telah menemukannya!"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You are repairing a room or simply welcoming family and don't want guests to "
"book it?<br/>Alternatively, you are closing for a week during an inter "
"season break?<br/>Let's have this reflected in your schedule!"
msgstr ""
"Anda sedang merenovasi kamar atau sekadar menyambut keluarga dan tidak ingin "
"tamu memesan kamar tersebut?<br/>Atau, Anda tutup selama seminggu saat jeda "
"antar musim?<br/>Mari kita buat hal ini terlihat di jadwal Anda!"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Semua Aplikasi yang terpasang di database Odoo Anda bisa diakses melalui "
"dasbor utama."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can as well select your company and in the Branches tab define branches."
msgstr ""
"Anda juga dapat memilih perusahaan dan mendefinisikan cabang di tab Cabang."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can find the participants and answers from the smart buttons of the "
"survey."
msgstr ""
"Peserta dan jawaban dapat ditemukan dengan mengakses tombol cerdas survei."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You completed that demo use case! There are millions of other ways to adapt "
"your\n"
"                    Odoo setup to fit your business needs."
msgstr ""
"Anda telah berhasil menyelesaikan contoh demo kasus penggunaan ini! Ada "
"banyak cara untuk menyesuaikan\n"
"                    pengaturan Odoo agar sesuai dengan kebutuhan bisnis Anda."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You could customize this section to add the identity document picture or "
"extra\n"
"                    fields at your convenience with studio. Just be careful, "
"such customizations can\n"
"                    quickly become messy."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menyesuaikan bagian ini untuk menambahkan gambar dokumen "
"identitas atau field tambahan\n"
"                    sesuai keinginan dengan studio. Namun, berhati-hatilah, "
"penyesuaian dapat\n"
"                    menjadi berantakan dalam sekejap."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps &gt; Industries "
"&gt;\n"
"                    Upgrade your package and check the related box"
msgstr ""
"Belum mengimpor data demo? Anda masih bisa melakukannya. Buka Aplikasi &gt; "
"Industri &gt;\n"
"                    Upgrade paket Anda dan centang kotak terkait"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "You have a future guest on the line willing to book a room?"
msgstr "Ada calon tamu yang sedang menelepon dan ingin memesan kamar?"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You have an hotel but may be providing numerous peripheral services and "
"offers.<br/>Here\n"
"            is how you might centralize those and bind them to your "
"customers in a single database."
msgstr ""
"Selain hotel, Anda mungkin juga menyediakan berbagai layanan dan penawaran "
"tambahan.<br/>Berikut\n"
"            cara untuk memusatkan dan menghubungkannya dengan pelanggan Anda "
"dalam satu database."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You just installed the Odoo for Hotel package. By doing so, we have "
"installed a\n"
"            bunch of necessary apps to run your Hotel efficiently."
msgstr ""
"Anda baru saja menginstal paket Odoo untuk Hotel. Dengan melakukan hal ini, "
"kami telah menginstal\n"
"            sejumlah aplikasi yang diperlukan untuk menjalankan Hotel Anda "
"secara efisien."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You may be running multiple places at the same time and most likely be "
"willing to run them all from the same database.<b/>We got you covered with "
"this using multiple companies or branches!"
msgstr ""
"Anda mungkin mengelola beberapa lokasi sekaligus dan ingin mengelola "
"semuanya dari database yang sama.<b/>Kami siap membantu dengan fitur ini "
"untuk mengelola beberapa perusahaan atau cabang!"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid "You might have tested this package with or without demo data."
msgstr "Anda mungkin sudah menguji paket ini dengan atau tanpa data demo."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You noticed that the Identity Check highlights whether you captured all the\n"
"            necessary information for a guest?"
msgstr ""
"Menyadari bahwa Pemeriksaan Identitas menyoroti apakah Anda telah menangkap "
"semua\n"
"            informasi yang diperlukan untuk tamu?"

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You now know how to create a new order.<br/>Let's replicate the previous "
"steps but\n"
"                this time, without confirming the order (just saving it as "
"draft)."
msgstr ""
"Anda kini tahu cara membuat pesanan baru.<br/>Mari ulangi langkah-langkah "
"sebelumnya,\n"
"                tapi kali ini tanpa mengonfirmasi pesanan (hanya "
"menyimpannya sebagai draf)."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You should be able to execute the following flows to have an overview of "
"various flows\n"
"            you can quickly execute with this package using Odoo."
msgstr ""
"Anda dapat menjalankan alur-alur berikut untuk melihat gambaran tentang "
"berbagai proses\n"
"            yang dapat dengan cepat dijalankan menggunakan paket ini di Odoo."

#. module: hotel
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:hotel.welcome_article_body
